T02TD2173E:341a-35: sgra snyan yid 'ong mchod pa dbul //

T02TD2173E:341b-0: bde gshegs thugs mchog rgyas gyur cig / sems dpa' chen po dang po mchog / dgyes chen rnams kyi @341b dga' ba che //
T02TD2173E:341b-1: kun du bzang po kun gyi bdag / rdo rje snyems pa bdag po'i bdag / thugs kyi sems dpa' ting 'dzin mchog / rdo rje'i rdo rje stobs po che //

T02TD2173E:342a-0: @342a * // 'di la the tshom byar mi rung //

T02TD2173E:342a-6: lhag ma rtse gsum lta bur bya //
T02TD2173E:342a-7: nyi mar zla ba bzhag nas ni //
T02TD2173E:342a-8: tshigs bcad 'di ni rjes su bzla /
T02TD2173E:342a-9: rin thang med pa'i dam pa'i chos //
T02TD2173E:342a-11: gzung dang mtshan ma rnam spangs pa //
T02TD2173E:342a-12: de nyid gnas la phyag 'tshal lo //

T02TD2173E:342a-14: nang gi 'khor lo gsal bsgoms nas //
T02TD2173E:342a-15: khrus ni rnam gsum bya bar gsungs //
T02TD2173E:342a-16: de nas rnal 'byor ci dgar rol //
T02TD2173E:342a-17: rdo rje sme gdung bshags pa ni //
T02TD2173E:342a-18: bdag cag rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos //
T02TD2173E:342a-19: bla ma yi dam lha dang ni //
T02TD2173E:342a-20: dkyil 'khor bzhugs pa'i spyan lam du //
T02TD2173E:342a-21: sngom pa gsum la gnas pa dang //

T02TD2173E:342a-25: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la //
T02TD2173E:342a-26: gshe zhing smad pa la sogs bshags //
T02TD2173E:342a-27: bde gshegs bka' yi chos rnams la //
T02TD2173E:342a-28: gzhung bzhin ma gyur 'khrul pa bshags //
T02TD2173E:342a-29: rnal 'byor lam gcig spun rnams la //
T02TD2173E:342a-30: rtsod pa la sogs bgyis pa bshags //

T02TD2173E:342b-2: bud med shes rab rang bzhin la //

T02TD2173E:342b-7: rdo rje slob dpon yi dam lha //

T02TD2173E:342b-9: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs bcas la //

T02TD2173E:342b-14: nan rtags chos rnams bgyis pa bshags //
T02TD2173E:342b-15: mi zab lam gcig spun rnams la //

T02TD2173E:342b-41: // / sbyin sreg las kyi cho ga ni //

T02TD2173E:343a-0: @343a * // de yang bzhi ru 'dus pa na //

T02TD2173E:343a-10: gtor ma phul bas sa rnams blang //
T02TD2173E:343a-11: khro bo'i las rnams thams cad pa'i //
T02TD2173E:343a-12: phyag rgya bcas nas sngags rnams brjod //
T02TD2173E:343a-13: thugs kyi 'od zer dag gis ni //
T02TD2173E:343a-14: sa rnams sbyang zhing byin gyis brlab //
T02TD2173E:343a-15: shin tu bsdus pa'i cho ga ni //
T02TD2173E:343a-16: 'od zer stobs kyi byin rlabs kyis //
T02TD2173E:343a-17: thab khung gang 'dod byin gyis brlab //
T02TD2173E:343a-18: mtshan ma la sogs dga' ba dang //
T02TD2173E:343a-19: rgyas par spro ba'i gang zag dang //

T02TD2173E:343a-22: mtshan ma la sogs mi dga' la //
T02TD2173E:343a-23: thab rnams bri 'am me tog dgram //
T02TD2173E:343a-24: rnal 'byor nus pa thob pa yis //
T02TD2173E:343a-25: rin chen snod du bya yang bzod //
T02TD2173E:343a-26: yang na de dag shes rab chung //
T02TD2173E:343a-27: rgyas pa mi nus dag la bstan //
T02TD2173E:343a-28: thab rnams bru ba'i rim pa yang ;
T02TD2173E:343a-29: / rgya ru ji tsam yod pa'i tshad //

T02TD2173E:343a-31: yang na sum cha bru ba'am //
T02TD2173E:343a-32: mtho gang dag tu bru ba'am //
T02TD2173E:343a-33: rgya yi tshad tsam bru ba ni //

T02TD2173E:343a-35: mkhas pa yis ni shes par bya //
T02TD2173E:343a-36: kha khyer mu ran tshad sogs kyang//
T02TD2173E:343a-37: so so'i gzhung dang mthun par bya //
T02TD2173E:343a-38: thab kyi dbyibs rnams bstan pa yang //

T02TD2173E:343a-40: rgyas pa gru bzhi'am rin chen dbyibs //

T02TD2173E:343a-46: gzhan yang thun mong las rnams la //
T02TD2173E:343a-47: zla ba kham pa lta bu'am //

T02TD2173E:343a-49: rdo rje lcags kyu la sogs su //
T02TD2173E:343a-50: mi 'dra thab kyi dbyibs bstan pa //
T02TD2173E:343b-0: rgyud rnams kun du shes @343b par bya //
T02TD2173E:343b-1: tshe bsring la sogs las la bsngags //
T02TD2173E:343b-2: thab kyi rgya yi tshad rnams kyang //
T02TD2173E:343b-3: khru bzhi khru gsum khru do dang //
T02TD2173E:343b-4: khru gang khru phyed sum cha'o //

T02TD2173E:343b-6: rgyud dang mthun par shes par bya //

T02TD2173E:343b-10: dbang la dmar po drag la gnag / las ni thams cad thab khung la //

T02TD2173E:344b-7: me lha'i rgyal po gzi brjid can //
T02TD2173E:344b-8: 'gro ba mi mthun gdul slad du //
T02TD2173E:344b-9: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs ston pa //
T02TD2173E:344b-10: las rnams kun mdzad khyod la 'dud //
T02TD2173E:344b-11: de ni thun mong gi bstod pa'o //
T02TD2173E:344b-12: khyad par gyi bstod pa ni rgyud du shes par bya'o //
T02TD2173E:344b-13: sbyin sreg gi las kyi rim pa ste bzhi pa'o /
T02TD2173E:344b-15: // / dang po yi ni rnal 'byor dang //
T02TD2173E:344b-16: rdo rje slob dpon byed pas su //
T02TD2173E:344b-17: bdag gzhan tshogs ni bsags pa'i phyir //
T02TD2173E:344b-18: slob dpon la ni srog lus dang //
T02TD2173E:344b-19: yul zhing sne bran chung mar bcas ;
T02TD2173E:344b-20: / sgyu ma'i sems kyis phul nas su //
T02TD2173E:344b-21: yang dang yang du gsol btab la //
T02TD2173E:344b-22: man ngag las kyi rim pa 'di //
T02TD2173E:344b-23: nyams su blang zhing the tshom gcad //
T02TD2173E:344b-24: de nas gzhung bzhin spyad par bya //
T02TD2173E:344b-25: de ltar byas na nges par ni //
T02TD2173E:344b-26: dngos grub rnam gnyis thob par 'gyur //
T02TD2173E:344b-27: drang ba'i don ni ma yin no //
T02TD2173E:344b-28: de ltar mi byed ser sna can //
T02TD2173E:344b-29: bdag 'dzin dam pos bzung nas su //
T02TD2173E:344b-30: slob dpon mnyes par mi 'gyur te //
T02TD2173E:344b-31: slob dpon mnyes par ma gyur na //
T02TD2173E:344b-32: dbang dang man ngag thob mi 'gyur //
T02TD2173E:344b-33: yang na man ngag thob nas kyang //
T02TD2173E:344b-34: slob dpon la ni rgyab kyis phyogs//
T02TD2173E:344b-35: dam tshig med par nyams pa ste //
T02TD2173E:344b-37: de nas rang gi rgyud brtags la //
T02TD2173E:344b-38: skyon de yod na spang bar bya'o //
T02TD2173E:344b-39: bdag gis 'gro ba'i don du ni //
T02TD2173E:344b-40: cho ga 'di brtsams dge ba yis //
T02TD2173E:344b-41: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
T02TD2173E:344b-42: bla med byang chub thob par shog / rdo rje las kyi tshogs rim par phye ba'i cho ga / slob dpon na bha bas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2173E:344b-44: // / lo ts'a ba khu ba b'irya dang /
T02TD2173E:344b-45: dge slong gzhon nu tshul khrims kyis bsgyur cing gtan la phab pa lags so /
